6... Qc7
{ We usually start with ...Qc7, so I am recommending this here as well. There is nothing wrong with   6...e5  either ,   nor with  6...Nf6  followed by ...Nd7 as described earlier. }
7. Be3 b6 8. Qd2 e5 9. O-O-O
